# Digital Library Book Management System

## Description
This system allows librarians to efficiently manage books, including adding, updating, searching, and deleting books. It maintains the availability status of each book.

## Features
- Add a book
- View all books
- Search for a book by ID or Title
- Update book details
- Delete a book record
- Exit system

